<h3 id="toc32"><span><strong>Player Name</strong></span></h3>
<p>Roget</p>
<h3 id="toc33"><span><strong>Name</strong></span></h3>
<p>Ted Mikelson</p>
<h3 id="toc34"><span><strong>Concept</strong></span></h3>
<p>Honest Newsman</p>
<h3 id="toc35"><span><strong>Power</strong></span></h3>
<p><strong>Trusted Anchorman:</strong> Ted is a veteran anchorman, who's had years of experience in the field and behind a camera. His authoritative yet soothing tones make people want to believe in him. Spending 1 AP to grants a +3 bonus to Persuasion and Perception.</p>
<h3 id="toc36"><span><strong>Aspects</strong></span></h3>
<p><strong>Asks the tough questions:</strong> Ted must always know the truth, and will go to great lengths to obtain a satisfactory understanding of the situation. This can lead to him finding information he'd rather not know, in places he doesn't like, accompanied by people who aren't thrilled with him.<br />
<strong>Lets go to Ted for a live report:</strong> Ted likes to explore any new area he is in to find new stuff. He tends to wander off.<br />
<strong>In Other News&#8230;:</strong> Ted has a tendency to distract or derail the conversations of people he talks to.</p>
<h3 id="toc37"><span><strong>Skills</strong></span></h3>
