</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ranged Weapons:</strong> <strong>2 (Fair)</strong></li>
<li><strong>Melee Weapons:</strong> <strong>1 (Average)</strong></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Physical Defense:</strong> <strong>2 (Fair)</strong></li>
<li><strong>Mental Defense:</strong> <strong>3 (Good)</strong></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Body:</strong> <strong>2 (Fair)</strong></li>
<li><strong>Mind:</strong> <strong>3 (Good)</strong></li>
</ul>
<ul>
