</ul>
<h3 id="toc38"><span><strong>Talents</strong></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Orators Voice:</strong> <strong>4 (Great)</strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc39"><span><strong>Possessions</strong></span></h3>
<p>Video Camera<br />
<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Microphone</span> Traded for a cassette recorder<br />
Pressed Suit<br />
Briefcase containing ream of papers, coffee mug, and video tapes.<br />
Small Knife<br />
9mm Pistol</p>
<h3 id="toc40"><span><strong>Personal History</strong></span></h3>
<p>Ted was a news reporter for a local station when disaster struck. He was one of the last reporters on the air before his station lost power, forcing him to flee.</p>
<h3 id="toc41"><span><strong>Miscellaneous</strong></span></h3>
<p>Ted is allergic to shellfish.</p>
